    #emph[It is very generous of you to offer me aid, but I promise there is nothing left that I need. I do, however, greatly enjoy reading your letters, so please send as many as you like. I promise to repay you with as many wildflowers from Lorwyn as I can gather.]

    #emph[Faithfully yours, Rhain]
]

